We're just at the beginning...

01:11:25.636 --> 01:11:28.639
and I don't expect
you or I to change...

01:11:28.723 --> 01:11:31.183
the course of where
our lives were headed...

01:11:31.267 --> 01:11:33.561
because of one date.

01:11:33.644 --> 01:11:38.107
