the Coalition of Evil...

01:12:34.455 --> 01:12:36.958
tried to ascertain the weakness
of every superhero...

01:12:37.041 --> 01:12:40.461
because they all have one, just like you.

01:12:40.544 --> 01:12:44.590
Your bones don't break.
